data.description:
Check out this charming 2 story home located minutes from Fort Cavazos, Killeen Airport, and various local restaurants/businesses. This beautiful home features an office/study room, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an open floor plan with a spacious living room, and an island concept kitchen. 
Upstairs you will find a spacious loft that is perfect for a family room/game room, a master suite with an enormous walk in closet, double vanity with jacuzzi tub and stand up shower. To make it even better, right off the master suite you will find a covered balcony for your morning coffee! This home is fully loaded and ready for a new home owner! Call your favorite realtor today to schedule a showing.
